      "factId": "hz.web.bbfe686cb4294c0d.fact.3",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "Captions not only display words as the textual equivalent of spoken dialogue or narration, but they also include non-dialogue information needed to understand the content, including speaker identification, sound effects, and music description.",
